OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781104294
OL,3,CMultiple attackers kill 12 people in
OL,4,Clate-night mass shooting in
OL,5,CJohannesburg
OL,7,FMultiple attackers killed 12 people
OL,8,Fand wounded at least nine in a late-
OL,9,Fnight mass shooting in Johannesburg,
OL,10,Fpolice said on Wednesday, the latest
OL,11,Fin such attacks that have shaken the
OL,12,FSouth African city.
OL,14,FPolice said they believe more than 10
OL,15,Fsuspects were driven in a minibus to
OL,16,Fan informal settlement in the
OL,17,FCleveland suburb of Johannesburg late
OL,18,Fon Tuesday night and once there,
OL,19,Fopened fire on people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
