OL,3,CMultiple attackers kill 12 people in
OL,4,Clate-night mass shooting in
OL,5,CJohannesburg
OL,7,FSouth Africa has seen several high-
OL,8,Fprofile mass shootings recently,
OL,9,Fincluding two in December that killed
OL,10,Fmore than 20 people. One of the
OL,11,Fattacks had also involved multiple
OL,12,Fshooters.
OL,14,FThe shootings are sometimes linked to
OL,15,Fillegal mining gangs that operate in
OL,16,Fand around Johannesburg. The suburb of
OL,17,FCleveland is connected to illegal
OL,18,Fmining activity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
