OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781104294
OL,3,CMultiple attackers kill 12 people in
OL,4,Clate-night mass shooting in
OL,5,CJohannesburg
OL,7,FAccording to a police statement, the
OL,8,Fattackers "moved through the area,
OL,9,Fopening fire on residents and
OL,10,Fcommunity members at multiple
OL,11,Flocations before fleeing the scene in
OL,12,Fthe same vehicle."
OL,14,FThe victims were nine men and three
OL,15,Fwomen, according to police. Eleven
OL,16,Fdied at the scene and another victim
OL,17,Fdied in the hospital.
