OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781104294
OL,3,CMultiple attackers kill 12 people in
OL,4,Clate-night mass shooting in
OL,5,CJohannesburg
OL,7,FPolice were searching for the
OL,8,Fattackers but no arrests had been
OL,9,Fmade. The motive for the shooting
OL,10,Fremained unclear, they said.
OL,12,FInformal settlements in South Africa
OL,13,Fare unplanned residential areas
OL,14,Fusually made up of shacks or similar
OL,15,Fstructures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
