OL,3,CMultiple attackers kill 12 people in
OL,4,Clate-night mass shooting in
OL,5,CJohannesburg
OL,7,F"Provincial and district detectives,
OL,8,Fsupported by crime intelligence and
OL,9,Fforensic experts, have been mobilized
OL,10,Fto investigate the incident and track
OL,11,Fdown the suspects," said police
OL,12,Fspokesperson Athlenda Mathe.
