PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781104294
OL,3,CMultiple attackers kill 12 people in
OL,4,Clate-night mass shooting in
OL,5,CJohannesburg
OL,7,FPolice commissioner Tommy Mthombeni
OL,8,Fsaid the attackers were "heartless"
OL,9,Fbut refused to link the killings to
OL,10,Fillegal mining until the
OL,11,Finvestigations was complete.
OL,13,F"We are still investigating, but what
OL,14,Fwe have seen here is a criminal act.
OL,15,FWe have deployed all required units,"
OL,16,Fhe said, adding that crime
OL,17,Fintelligence officials have also been
OL,18,Fdeployed to the area.
